artistSections:
### La Texana
- **YouTube**: [Search on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=La+Texana)
- **Link**: [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/latexana.a)
- **Genres**: Post-Punk
- **Bio**: La Texana is a Tijuana-based band known for their post-punk Mexicano sound with sparse guitar lines and stark, spoken-sung lyrics.

### Gabi Bravo
- **YouTube**: [Search on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Gabi+Bravo)
- **Link**: [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/gabi.bravomusic)
- **Genres**: Synthpop, Latinx, Electronic
- **Bio**: Gabi Bravo is a Latina singer-songwriter from Watsonville, California, known for blending ethereal synths with emotionally charged lyrics.

### LAHORKA
- **YouTube**: [Search on YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=LAHORKA)
- **Link**: [Bandcamp](https://lahorka.bandcamp.com/)
- **Genres**: Experimental Pop, Ambient, Synthpunk
- **Bio**: LAHORKA is an Oakland/Puerto Rico-based synthpunk duo creating unique sonic experiences influenced by their Puerto Rican roots.
